  <div class="text-content">
    <p>So here we are, the new website has launched. I have tried to keep it as simple as possible, like the last one.</p>

<p>It still a WIP at present and I am writing up some fresh content.</p>

<p>After the last year, with COVID and everything else thats been going on I felt like it was time for a change.</p>

<p>The revamp of the site is just the start of some exciting things to happen this year. I wanted to make it more my personal site, to showcase some of the things I have been working on.</p>

